        </mj-text>
        <mj-text padding="10px 12px" font-family="Roboto+Serif" color="#000000">
          <p style="font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.4;filter:blur(5px);">Vertex Pharmaceuticals has <a href="https://link.longandshort.com/ls-31-01-2025-h2-2-received-fda-approval?source=website" target="_blank">received FDA approval</a> for its new painkiller. Journavx offers a safer alternative to addictive opioids through its unique functionality. The drug blocks pain signals in nerve cells without entering the brain. This reduces the risk of addiction significantly. The drug is priced at $15.50 per 50mg tablet. While there are high expectations around the success of the drug, the commercialization process could be challenging given the availability of cheaper and widely used opioids.
          </p>
